<div class="new-job">


    <p class="new-job-desc">
        你張貼的工作會在這個網站上停留三十天，三十天過後這個徵才啟事會過期，你可以隨時再回來重新張貼工作廣告。
    </p>

    <br><br>
    <h3> STEP 1 : 撰寫工作內容 </h3>

    <hr>



    <br><br>

    <form accept-charset="UTF-8" action="/jobs/preview" class="simple_form form-horizontal" id="new_job" method="post" novalidate="novalidate">
        <div style="display:none"><input name="utf8" type="hidden" value="&#x2713;" /><input name="authenticity_token" type="hidden" value="vzK0/3hWVlbhZkjZQ1v72Xdp8itx3EYilD9kpLTpJ7M=" /></div>




        <h4 class="instruction"> &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;第一步，告訴我們詳細資訊 </h4>


        <div class="form-group string required job_title"><label class="string required col-sm-2 control-label" for="job_title"><abbr title="required">*</abbr> Job Title</label><div class="col-sm-10"><input class="string required form-control" id="job_title" name="job[title]" type="text" /><p class="help-block">“Senior Designer” or “Rails Programmer”</p></div></div>


        <div class="form-group radio_buttons optional job_category_id"><label class="radio_buttons optional col-sm-2 control-label">Category</label><div class="col-sm-10"><span class="radio"><label for="job_category_id_8" name="job[category_id]"><input class="radio_buttons optional" id="job_category_id_8" name="job[category_id]" type="radio" value="8" />醫療</label></span><span class="radio"><label for="job_category_id_2" name="job[category_id]"><input checked="checked" class="radio_buttons optional" id="job_category_id_2" name="job[category_id]" type="radio" value="2" />程式設計</label></span><span class="radio"><label for="job_category_id_7" name="job[category_id]"><input class="radio_buttons optional" id="job_category_id_7" name="job[category_id]" type="radio" value="7" />其他</label></span><span class="radio"><label for="job_category_id_4" name="job[category_id]"><input class="radio_buttons optional" id="job_category_id_4" name="job[category_id]" type="radio" value="4" />市場開發 / 業務</label></span><span class="radio"><label for="job_category_id_9" name="job[category_id]"><input class="radio_buttons optional" id="job_category_id_9" name="job[category_id]" type="radio" value="9" />電子業</label></span><span class="radio"><label for="job_category_id_3" name="job[category_id]"><input class="radio_buttons optional" id="job_category_id_3" name="job[category_id]" type="radio" value="3" />網路行銷</label></span><span class="radio"><label for="job_category_id_1" name="job[category_id]"><input class="radio_buttons optional" id="job_category_id_1" name="job[category_id]" type="radio" value="1" />視覺設計</label></span><span class="radio"><label for="job_category_id_6" name="job[category_id]"><input class="radio_buttons optional" id="job_category_id_6" name="job[category_id]" type="radio" value="6" />行銷 / 企劃</label></span><span class="radio"><label for="job_category_id_5" name="job[category_id]"><input class="radio_buttons optional" id="job_category_id_5" name="job[category_id]" type="radio" value="5" />網站內容編輯</label></span></div></div>


        <div class="form-group integer optional job_lower_bound">
            <label class="integer optional col-sm-2 control-label" for="job_lower_bound">薪水</label><div class="col-sm-10">
                <div class="input-prepend input-append">
                    <input class="string optional" id="job_lower_bound" name="job[lower_bound]" placeholder="下限 (Lower bound)" type="text" /> ~
                    <input class="string optional" id="job_higher_bound" name="job[higher_bound]" placeholder="上限 (Higher bound)" type="text" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group string required job_location"><label class="string required col-sm-2 control-label" for="job_location"><abbr title="required">*</abbr> 工作地點</label><div class="col-sm-10"><input class="string required form-control" id="job_location" name="job[location]" type="text" /><p class="help-block">臺北 / 高雄 / 上海 / ...etc.</p></div></div>

        <div class="form-group text required job_description">
            <label class="text required col-sm-2 control-label" for="job_description"><abbr title="required">*</abbr> 工作敘述</label><div class="col-sm-10">
                <textarea class="text required form-control" data-provide="markdown" id="job_description" name="job[description]" rows="10">
</textarea><p class="help-block">使用 Markdown 語法</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group text required job_apply_instruction">
            <label class="text required col-sm-2 control-label" for="job_apply_instruction"><abbr title="required">*</abbr> 如何應徵</label><div class="col-sm-10">
                <textarea class="text required form-control" id="job_apply_instruction" name="job[apply_instruction]" rows="3">
</textarea><p class="help-block">Example: Send a resume to hr@mycompany.com</p>
            </div>
        </div>


        <h4 class="instruction"> &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;介紹你的公司 </h4>

        <br><br>


        <div class="form-group string optional job_company_name"><label class="string optional col-sm-2 control-label" for="job_company_name">公司 / 組織名稱</label><div class="col-sm-10"><input class="string optional col-lg-4 form-control" id="job_company_name" name="job[company_name]" type="text" /><p class="help-block">Enter your company or organization’s name.</p></div></div>

        <div class="form-group url optional job_url"><label class="url optional col-sm-2 control-label" for="job_url">URL</label><div class="col-sm-10"><input class="string url optional form-control" id="job_url" name="job[url]" type="url" /></div></div>
        <div class="form-group email optional job_email"><label class="email optional col-sm-2 control-label" for="job_email">Email</label><div class="col-sm-10"><input class="string email optional form-control" id="job_email" name="job[email]" type="email" /><p class="help-block">This is where we’ll send your receipt and confirmation email.</p></div></div>


        <hr>

        <div class="form-group text optional job_description">
            <label class="text optional col-sm-1 control-label" for="job_description"></label>
            <div class="col-sm-11">
                <input class="btn btn-lg btn-danger" name="commit" type="submit" value="預覽徵才啟事" />
            </div>
        </div>


    </form>


</div>



